722010f.text:
Orchard Street, west side, north from (Nos. 123-25), but not including Delancey to East Houston Streets. Shown is a pushcart market a feature of this east side locality. In fact, the street name itself is synonymous with
this mercantile endeavor.
About 1910.
Ewing dalloway.
Ncw ~2S67
